===2010 census===
As of the [[census]]<ref name="wwwcensusgov">{{cite web|title=U.S. Census website|url=https://www.census.gov|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|access-date=2012-07-08}}</ref> of 2010, there were 183 people, made up of 100 males (54.64%) and 83 females (45.36%). The [[population density]] was 29.9 per square mile.<ref>Census Viewer http://censusviewer.com/city/MO/Ozora</ref>
The racial makeup of the village was 97.81% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]], 1.64% American Indian and Alaska native, and 0.55% from [[Race (U.S. Census)|other races]].<ref>U.S.Census.gov https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/cph-2-27.pdf</ref>

